DESCRIPTION:Join us on Tuesday\, July 14\, from 4 - 8 PM at Whispering Vine Fourth St. for a Flights & Flatbread tasting featuring Groth with special guest Ted Henry\, Director of Winegrowing.\nTasting Fee: $45 per person Includes the flight and one flatbread.\nReserve your Spot: https://www.exploretock.com/whisperingvine4thstreet/experience/540467/flights-flatbread-tasting-groth\nFeatured Wines:\n- Groth Reserve Cabernet Sauvignon 2022 – Winery $190\n- Groth Oakcross 2020 – Winery $110\n- Groth Cabernet Sauvignon 2022 – Winery $80\n- Groth Oakville Estate Sauvignon Blanc 2023 – Winery $65\nFlight and flatbread included.
